{
  "stem": "3658.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, if you-- if you-- but it was warm and you-- you were happy to have something in the stomach.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after-- after a while working there-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this story is something which-- I must tell you what happened to me there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were working underground, and it was very stick-- stifling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was hot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and tired.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were tired.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At night we worked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a-- a shocking, shocking place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you stood with shovels and shoveling on this sand, this special sand, on a belt.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, it was a sort of a conveyor belt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there weren't so many guards around there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because it was a long area, and we were lots and lots of people there from the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you look around, and you see that there are not many people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the guy that-- in-- in twos, always, you know, one for one side and the other shoveling on the stuff.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said to the guy, you go under the belt, because it was low.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, we dig from under the belt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you have a little sleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, after a few-- an hour or so, I'll wake you, and I'll go and have a sleep.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I-- he went and he had a sleep.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I woke him up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then, I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I tell you, I remember the most beautiful dream when I was at home among the family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And suddenly, I was punched.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He-- he forgot about me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was [GERMAN], you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Appel-- Appel.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As soon as you come out of the mine, and they count you as you go in, and they count you as you go out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So of course, I copped it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He-- he forgot to wake you?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
